          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Roasted Chicken with Rosemary Roast Potatoes. A British home-cook's dish — the kind of recipe families adjust across generations. Adjustable for what you need."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A weeknight-friendly recipe: most of the work is the prep, and the cooking takes care of itself."
          }
        ]
